    "As a result, CoBDock has undergone testing on notable benchmarks, namely DUDE and CASF-2016, which are recognized for their size and prominence.",
    "Additionally, three supplementary benchmarks have been utilized to provide further insight into the capabilities of CoBDock.",
    "Comparison with state-of-the-art methodsCoBDock contains two cavity detection tools, Fpocket and P2Rank, used to determine the binding site.",
    "Besides the unique features of Fpocket and P2Rank discussed above, they have significant cavity identification performance, especially P2Rank.",
    "P2Rank surpasses a number of currently available tools, such as two commonly used standalone programs (Fpocket and SiteHound), a thorough consensus-based tool (MetaPocket 2.0) (Additional file 1: Table S3), and a recent deep learning-based method (DeepSite)."
